io.craigmiller160.school.repo

Class JoinHolderDaoIT

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.craigmiller160.school.repo.JoinHolderDaoIT

  • @ContextConfiguration(value="classpath:/test-context.xml")
public class JoinHolderDaoIT
extends java.lang.Object
    An integration test for the JoinHolder entity DAO used by this application. Because JoinHolders operations must be tested using the entities being joined to ensure all the DAO methods are working properly, this is a LARGE test class, with many tests in it.

    Because JoinHolder entities depend on the entities they are being joined with, this test cannot succeed if the integration tests for the DAOs for the entities being joined do not succeed as well. If the other DAOs do not work, then join operations cannot be successfully tested.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    craig
